    <article id="post-4646" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/4646.html" rel="bookmark">Laravel 5.2 后台开发实例 —— 基于权限自动生成面包屑及菜单栏</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-05-31T00:15:40+08:00">2016-05-31</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-05-31T10:52:01+08:00">2016-05-31 10:52:01</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/big-pang">
                            big-pang
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    16118 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/4646.html#comments">
                        36 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/4646.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/687474703a2f2f6f377a65376f7034742e626b742e636c6f7564646e2e636f6d2f515125453625383825414125453525394225424532303136303533303136333131322e706e67-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/4646.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="1920" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/687474703a2f2f6f377a65376f7034742e626b742e636c6f7564646e2e636f6d2f515125453625383825414125453525394225424532303136303533303136333131322e706e67-1920x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>简介
基于Laravel 5.2 与 zizaco/entrust 权限管理、开箱即用的后台模板，面包屑、菜单栏都是基于权限来生成，集成了laravel-debugbar 超好用调试工具，带有日志解析查看模块。
截图



源码地址
https://github.com/big-pang/laravel5.2-Admin
安装

	git clone 到本地
	执行...</p>
        </div>

