    <article id="post-3602" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/3602.html" rel="bookmark">安装 Laravel 出问题了？你可能需要修改 composer.json 文件</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-03-17T10:09:59+08:00">2016-03-17</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-03-17T10:20:20+08:00">2016-03-17 10:20:20</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    2663 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/3602.html#comments">
                        1 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/3602.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/2015-11-23_231242-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/3602.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="568" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/2015-11-23_231242-568x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>Composer最近对pre-update-command的工作方式做了修改，该项修改会导致Laravel安装失败。

Jordi Boggiano给出了修改的原因：
如果没有composer.lock文件，初始化的“install”执行的实际是update操作，这会触发pre-update-cmd，而在此修改之前是触发pre-install-cmd。
幸运的是修复这一失败很简单...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
