    <article id="post-3285" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/3285.html" rel="bookmark">Ubuntu 下快速部署安装 Apache + PHP + MySQL + phpMyAdmin 笔记</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-02-06T13:50:03+08:00">2016-02-06</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-02-06T13:50:47+08:00">2016-02-06 13:50:47</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    5380 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/3285.html#comments">
                        1 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/3285.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/lamp-mysql-php-apache1-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/3285.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/lamp-mysql-php-apache1-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>

安装 Apache
sudo apt-get install apache2
为了确定安装是否成功，我们来测试一下。打开浏览器，输入以下网址:
http://localhost/
如果成功，你会看到以下内容 &quot;It works!&quot; , 祝贺你，第一步，你算是跨出去了。

安装 PHP5

在终端输入以下命令:
sudo apt-get install php5 ...</p>
        </div>

